<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-title>Welcome to Recontent.app</mj-title>
    <mj-attributes>
      <mj-all font-family="Helvetica, sans-serif"></mj-all>
      <mj-text
        font-weight="400"
        font-size="16px"
        color="#616161"
        line-height="24px"
      ></mj-text>
      <mj-section padding="0px"></mj-section>
    </mj-attributes>
  </mj-head>

  <mj-body background-color="#fdfdfc">
    <mj-section padding-top="50px">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-image
          align="left"
          src="https://cdn.recontent.app/emails/logo.png"
          width="140px"
        ></mj-image>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section padding-top="30px">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text
          color="#353431"
          font-weight="600"
          line-height="20px"
          font-size="32px"
        >
          Welcome to
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text
          color="#501A48"
          font-weight="600"
          line-height="20px"
          font-size="32px"
        >
          Recontent.app 🚀
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section padding-top="30px">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text color="#706f6c">
          Thanks for being one of Recontent.app earliest supporters. My goal is
          simple: helping you localise & distribute your product's content.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text color="#706f6c">
          In 2022, you should not have to ask developers (or get asked) to
          update hardcoded strings or pay hundreds of bucks per month to
          collaborate with your team on localisation.
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text color="#706f6c" padding-bottom="0px">
          With Recontent.app, the objective is clear:
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text color="#706f6c" padding-top="0px">
          <ul>
            <li>⚡️ Unlimited everything, pay-as-you-go pricing</li>
            <li>🚀 Projects, tasks, experimentations to iterate quickly</li>
            <li>🔌 Open platform, in & out with your tools</li>
            <li>🌱 And more based on your needs!</li>
          </ul>
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text color="#706f6c">
          Please don't hesitate to reply to this email with your expectations &
          experiences with other tools.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#706f6c">
          Until the next one, have a wonderful day,
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section padding-top="20px">
      <mj-column width="11%">
        <mj-image
          padding-right="0px"
          padding-left="25px"
          border-radius="50%"
          align="left"
          width="70px"
          src="https://cdn.recontent.app/emails/gregoire-mielle-avatar.jpeg"
        ></mj-image>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="89%" padding-left="12px" padding-top="3px">
        <mj-text padding="0" color="#706f6c" line-height="8px">
          <p>Grégoire Mielle</p>
          <p style="font-size: 14px">
            <a
              style="color: #501a48; text-decoration: none"
              href="https://recontent.app"
              >Recontent.app</a
            >
            founder
          </p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section padding-top="10px">
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-color="#E0E0E0"></mj-divider>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
